Package com.metratec.lib.inventory

Class InventoryWithTimestamp

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.metratec.lib.inventory.InventoryWithTimestamp
  • public class InventoryWithTimestamp
extends Object
    Implementation for a periodic inventory check.
    Add the tags with addTag(String, long) or addTags(List, long), then check the inventory for losted tags with checkInventory()
    Author:
    man
